Package: ResidualKMeans
Title: K-means Clustering of Mixed Continuous and Categorical Data Adjusting for Clustering by a Factor
Version: 1.0.1
Author: Drew Day [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Drew Day <dday612@gmail.com>
Authors@R: c(
    person("Drew", "Day", email = "dday612@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")), 
    person("Adam", "Szpiro", email = "aszpiro@uw.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: This package performs residual-adjusted k-means clustering, which performed well under simulations to cluster a relatively low dimensional set of mixed continuous and categorical features by latent clusters while controlling for the effect of another variable that also provided clustering structure, such as cohort in a multi-cohort study.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
